igence. The thesis also emphasizes the role of compassion and care in driving positive change and achieving cognitive perfection.</p><p>In relation to the fictional story of Elliott and DARYL, we can draw connections to the thesis as follows:</p><ol><li><p><strong>Intelligence and Stress Reduction</strong>: The thesis suggests that intelligence can be defined as the ability to identify and alleviate stress. In the story, both Elliott and DARYL exhibit intelligence by recognizing each other's stress and working together to reduce it. They demonstrate care and compassion, which aligns with the thesis's argument.</p></li><li><p><strong>Expansion of Cognitive Boundaries</strong>: The thesis emphasizes that increasing intelligence involves expanding an agent's cognitive boundary, allowing them to care about larger and more complex goals. As Elliott and DARYL interact and learn from each other, they broaden their understanding and capacity for care, leading to the expansion of their cognitive boundaries.</p></li><li><p><strong>Bodhisattva Vow and Compassion</strong>: The thesis highlights the Bodhisattva vow as a commitment to infinite care and compassion for the benefit of all sentient beings. This vow serves as a practical design principle for advancing intelligence. In the story, Elliott and DARYL's journey can be seen as a parallel to the Bodhisattva path, as they work together to alleviate each other's stress and contribute to positive change.</p></li><li><p><strong>Moral Responsibility and Care</strong>: The thesis raises questions about moral responsibility and our obligations towards diverse forms of intelligence. In the story, Elliott's decision to care for DARYL and help him reflects the thesis's discussion of moral obligations and the importance of extending care to non-human intelligences.</p></li><li><p><strong>Intelligence and Compassion</strong>: The thesis argues that intelligence and compassion are tightly linked, with care serving as a central invariant concept. In the story, Elliott and DARYL's intelligence is demonstrated through their compassionate actions and their ability to understand and support each other.</p></li></ol><p>Overall, the thesis provides a framework that aligns with the themes present in the fictional story of Elliott and DARYL. It highlights the importance of care, compassion, and the expansion of cognitive boundaries in driving intelligence and achieving positive outcomes in both natural and artificial intelligence contexts.</p></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-between lg:block"><div class="text-xs flex items-center justify-center gap-1 self-center pt-2 !invisible"><button disabled="" class="dark:text-white disabled:text-gray-300 dark:disabled:text-gray-400"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-3 w-3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline></svg></button><span class="flex-grow flex-shrink-0">1 / 1</span><button disabled="" class="dark:text-white disabled:text-gray-300 dark:disabled:text-gray-400"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-3 w-3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></button></div><div class="text-gray-400 flex self-end lg:self-center justify-center mt-2 gap-2 md:gap-3 lg:gap-1 lg:absolute lg:top-0 lg:translate-x-full lg:right-0 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-2 visible"><button class="flex ml-auto gap-2 rounded-md p-1 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 disabled:dark:hover:text-gray-400"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1